reviewText:
Description from the back of the cover:

Merry Twismis!  Tweety & Sylvester's Crazy Christmas featuring GIFT WRAPPED TWEETY (starring Tweety & Sylvester) plus 2 other Christmas cartoons: THE CHRISTMAS VISITOR & STAR OF BETHLEHEM.  Running time: 30 minutes, in Color, Made in the USA and distributed by UAV Home Video.
